    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: The guilty suspect is Petra Sloan, slot 3. Evidence 1 places Petra at the
    route terminal during the undocumented transfer gap. Evidence 2 matches sable
    cartridge dust in the seam of Petra's folio strap. Evidence 3 links a torn tamper-fiber
    snag from her cuff to the missing cartridge sleeve.
